- Checks that declared face normals are consistent with the normal
  implied by vertex winding order (cross-product check).
- Also checks for degenerate triangles (zero-area faces).
- Retains all original checks: manifold/open-edges, parse errors, etc.

Usage:
    python stl_validator_improved.py <file.stl>
